@* Route entry page for alternate side-nav layout demo. *@
<section class="panel">
    <h2>Layout Swap Demo</h2>
    <p>This page uses an alternate layout with a side nav instead of the top demo nav as its local chrome.</p>
    <div class="demo-note" role="note">
        <strong>How To Test:</strong> navigate here from top nav, then use side-nav links and return to
        <code>Server Trigger</code>. The app shell remains stable while <code>#hrx-main-layout</code> swaps.
    </div>
</section>

<section class="panel">
    <h3>Why This Matters</h3>
    <p class="demo-caption">
        It proves HyperRazor is swapping route content consistently even when those routes carry different
        page-level layout wrappers.
    </p>
</section>
